---
title: "Convert Albumin Concentration Units"
description: "Convert Albumin Concentration Units."
pagefind: true
---







## Usage

```r

convert_alb(alb)
```


## Arguments

<div class="arg-table">
<table>
<thead>
<tr><th>Argument</th><th>Description</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>alb</code></td>
<td>albumin concentration (g/L)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>


## Value

Albumin concentration (g/dL)


## Description

Convert Albumin Concentration Units


## Examples

```r

convert_alb(40)

df <- data.frame(
  ID = c(1, 2, 3, 4),
  ALB = c(35, 40, 28, 45)
)

df <- df %>%
  dplyr::group_by(ID) %>%
  dplyr::mutate(ALBBL = convert_alb(ALB))
df
```


